{"tid":2456983,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【國際夢工場・沈旭暉】 國際象棋冠軍梁浩恩： 《后翼棄兵》的國際關係有多真實？（上）","createTime":"2021-03-22T10:09:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-22T10:09:01.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"72434692311f7837ee716f679b907cc1d5681634","tid":2456983,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T10:09:01.000Z","msg":"【國際夢工場・沈旭暉 009🇺🇸🇷🇺】<br />\n國際象棋冠軍梁浩恩：<br />\n《后翼棄兵》的國際關係有多真實？（上）<br />\nMar 10, 2021<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=p6PpCOpG1PY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dp6PpCOpG1PY&d=Hu0SY4Cx1oodln7cCHpxbWzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=df29e2da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=p6PpCOpG1PY</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n堅離地球 &middot; 沈旭暉<br />\n195K subscribers<br />\n<br />\n以冷戰期間國際象棋大賽為背景的Netflix劇集《后翼棄兵》(The Queen's Gambit)，在全球掀起一陣國際象棋熱。究竟這門智力運動在國際競賽的真實狀況如何？在冷戰背景下，美蘇的國際象棋較量充滿哪些象徵意義？這次請了政治系畢業、曾獲香港國際象棋錦標賽冠軍的梁浩恩 (Andrew) 和我們分享，希望能協助大家觀賞時多看門道。<br />\n<br />\nSimon 沈旭暉 堅離地 Social Media ▶<br />\n⏺Patreon: <a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/simonshen​​​​\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.patreon.com%2Fsimonshen%E2%80%8B%E2%80%8B%E2%80%8B%E2%80%8B&d=Hu0SY4Cx1oodln7cCHpxbWzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=f76347a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.patreon.com/simonshen​​​​</a><br />\n🔼Facebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/shensimon​​​​\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fshensimon%E2%80%8B%E2%80%8B%E2%80%8B%E2%80%8B&d=Hu0SY4Cx1oodln7cCHpxbWzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=43408281\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/shensimon​​​​</a><br />\nℹ️Instagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/simon.diplo...​\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fsimon.diplo...%E2%80%8B&d=Hu0SY4Cx1oodln7cCHpxbWzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=81fec4e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https:/